00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] mogo mi je, bar da on preživi?"

173
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovih koji su ga poznavali.

174
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,000
