176
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Mama, izajte, predajte se."

177
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja odmah ustanem,

178
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] izađem iz podroma,

179
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,000
