182
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Moga Tomu, ubile iz predkuće."

183
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u mogu dragana,

184
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,000
