00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] pa ona će nas onoko striljati.

375
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tako, sve to je se...

376
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ste se vi osjećali u tom trenu?

377
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jel ste bili prestrašeni?

378
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, nisam.

379
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili mi je Bog dao snagu?

380
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi je dao snagu.

381
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja samo kažem,

382
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] mene je Bog spasio i molitva.

383
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što sam vas da Boga molila,

384
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] išli smo u crkvu.

385
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moje Darko je išao u godini u crkvu,

386
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] više i već godana u godini bilo.

387
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ujutru i na večer.

388
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trinijest utara,

389
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo vas da postrali sve tomanti,

390
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] išli na misu i trinijest subota.

391
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na zornicu,

392
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] svako jutro su išli u školu.

393
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] svako jutro su išli na zornicu.

394
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ustane na mireštalu,

395
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] nija probudi,

396
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja oti idem na zornicu,

397
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne za mno gore na zornicu.

398
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svako jutro.

399
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da smo bili...

400
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I mene je majka umrla od 46. godine.

401
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bila samoudala.

402
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Brat mi najstariji je bio u vojske.

403
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sestra mi ostala od 16 mjeseci.

404
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moje ibe pokojnje je bilo 11 mjeseci.

405
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ta 4-5 puta unesec padala.

406
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tata mi umroo nakon 7 godina materije.

407
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta se gubila unesec, padala.

408
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rođak, jedan otetke mi umroo,

409
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] što mi je bila maćeha.

410
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tada bio Andrej moj pokojnji sa mnom.

411
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovde u grobljom bili.

412
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tad oni se ispadali.

413
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dali oni meni u limonadu

414
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam se ja povratila.

415
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on meni govori pokojnje duši.

416
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže:

417
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne daj Bože mile da ti dočekaš

418
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] da meni nešto bude.

419
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti za mno živa u grobljom."

420
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] A tada sam me to dočekala

421
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] to da sam to videla

422
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] i sina kako su ga ubili

423
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] i sve.

424
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kako je mene ova jedna žena rekla

425
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam čula Rafale.

426
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] I videla sam ovog jednog njegovu pušku.

427
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Reko: "Gori su ga ubili."

428
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ova žena kad su nju gori vodili

429
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] ovi vojnici

430
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] došla i mene vako šapće.

431
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže:

432
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Mile, videla sam te Andriju,

433
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] ublega na dnu odnika

434
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] ovome."

435
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I govor sve odnešeno.

436
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja nakon ništa.

437
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo Bože, ti daje samo snage

438
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se ovo uzdrži.

439
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta god budi.

440
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni opet nas...

441
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tad su zapravo evo

442
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] spustilo se i vaš sin

443
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ostali vojnici.

444
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Očekivali su da će se poštivati

445
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] ženevska konvencija.

446
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, ženevska konvencija.

447
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Podle su mene pitali

448
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako...

449
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tako taj tipo rekao

450
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] i to je tako bilo.

451
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su odna ovoga

452
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] stipo policajice ozvali

453
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] gore u našu kuću

454
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] i mojega Sandriju

455
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] ubili na dnu odnika kuće.

456
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] A njega su ovako gore

457
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] na vrodnika.

458
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stipo policajica.

459
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I taj dan padala je kiša.

460
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je danas ništa šta ne pada.

461
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Taj dan kiša padala

462
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] na mene je samo bila

463
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] vako majica

464
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] bez ovoga džempera.

465
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I poluver bio.

466
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Džemper sam bila,

467
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] uzela,

468
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] čerku ogranila.

469
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo bili svi mokri.

470
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su nas uzgonili,

471
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,000
