472
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo neđe.

473
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sada oni će nas iše.

474
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pobići je nas.

475
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo tiza.

476
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni postrojile nas.

477
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dođeš ove druge žene od ozdoluda

478
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] doveli iz Kreša.

479
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] ova djeca,

480
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad su videli čeče tamo po onome.

481
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,000
