486
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] kaže sada,

487
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] trebat će nam za drugi put.

488
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su...

489
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da vas ostave na životu

490
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,000
