491
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja za drugi put.

492
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moga je to,

493
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:48,000
[UNKNOWN] moja draga,

494
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] nije imao tada 14,5 godina,

495
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] a ti bi rekao da nije imao 18, 20 godina.

496
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je bio krupan i sve.

497
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] i njega jedan odvojio,

498
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] aj kaže tamo,

499
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] bar da ti ostaneš.

500
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da je draga moj tada ona ostao,

501
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Andrejanom isto,

502
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ona sa mnom bila,

503
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,000
