508
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] nije mogla skiniti.

509
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova jedan došla,

510
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] ona je sa sad tresla,

511
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] govori ova njoj.

512
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je bio ovaj...

513
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu vojnik kaže,

514
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] kance, djeteta kaže,

515
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] ona je i ona skinula krunicu,

516
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako su je braća nosila krunicu,

517
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] nosila i ona.

518
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ona je ona kako je uzela,

519
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] skinula krunicu,

520
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,000
