521
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] i počela ovako gazeta,

522
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono, dole zemlji,

523
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ona je otišla,

524
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] ovako je utrila,

525
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] i taj momak uzuo krunicu,

526
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] obriso je dao Andrejanin star,

527
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, sine Udžev,

528
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] i on je rekao da ima i on dvoje,

529
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] dvije čerke,

530
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je njega to posjećalo.

531
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, taj musliman.

532
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Taj musliman, ja.

533
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je našao neko da je bio čovječan.

534
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čovječan, da.

535
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su,

536
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,000
