537
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ovaj jedan govori,

538
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] odvojite kaže žene i djecu,

539
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] trebat će nam za drugi put.

540
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] i mi smo odvojili,

541
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] nas odvojili,

542
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] iza ove kuće,

543
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,000
