544
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rafale su popocali,

545
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] nija je tu,

546
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,000
