547
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] pobijeni.

548
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj jedan oteci,

549
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja mi sin počeo bježati,

550
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] njega su ovako dolubili,

551
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] ispod.

552
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Andreje skočio iz jednog zida,

553
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] i onda nas opet vrati.

554
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tad je vaš sin Ivan?

555
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja tu je strijeljan.

556
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se to dogodilo?

557
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste vidjeli taj dobro?

558
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesmo.

559
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je pred vama strijeljan?

560
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije pred nama,

561
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] nas su samo iza kuće odvojili,

562
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:28,000
