568
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] i oni su ovako ležali doli,

569
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji nisu bili u skuću.

570
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su ležali,

571
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,000
