575
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vako mu ruke bile.

576
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tam u toj kući smo opet bili tu,

577
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:50,000
