582
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tu nešto što je bilo ove municije,

583
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] odnaši ja uzeli,

584
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] i oni su ponijeli to gore,

585
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] i moja Andreina mogla ići još od ove jedne jele,

