[SPEAKER_00] izvedli ga,

1425
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] nije više ni dolazio.

1426
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] I posle se ove pitali,

1427
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] šta oni mogu, znaš, napraviti.

1428
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima lišta doda što sam ja pričala.

1429
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova jedna rekao,

1430
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] mi nemamo ništa na dodati,

1431
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako god gospođa pričala,

1432
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] sve je nako bilo.

1433
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da...

1434
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači priznali su.

1435
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve su priznali.

1436
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi su priznali.

1437
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi su priznali.

1438
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Misli li su oni smijeći da zna,

1439
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja imam iskaz.

1440
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vazda kako sam davila prvi put ovde

1441
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] u Spritu u Zagrebu,

1442
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] vas da mi iskazali.

1443
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek isti iskaz.

1444
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek isti iskaz.

1445
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja vas reknu,

1446
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne daj Bože da je moj ko radio njima,

1447
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] šta su oni radili.

1448
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Meni...

1449
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] A zapravo jedna rečenica

1450
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] koju ste rekli je meni tu bila isto znakovita,

1451
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] nejako se kasnije kroz Haški tribunal

1452
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] i suđenje Seferu Haliloviću

1453
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] željelo prikazati kako

1454
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] neretve akcija nije ni bilo

1455
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kako nije željeli učiniti se to etničko čištenje Hrvata.

1456
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Upravo to su oni rekli kad su upali u vašu kuću.

1457
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Do neuma ćemo sve očistiti.

1458
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve očistiti, ja.

1459
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ko preživi morat će preći na islam.

1460
00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na islam.

1461
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] To sam ja suđu.

1462
00:41:59,000 --> 00:42:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja i danas suđu.

1463
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tako reknem i pred muslimanima i sve.

1464
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni se divije kako ja mogu tako pričati.

1465
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mene su nije ove žene govorile.

1466
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da su njima radili šta su meni radili.

1467
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da oni ne mogli sa njima ni pričati ni raditi ni ništa.

1468
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja mogu meni savješ čista, mirno spavam.

1469
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I nemate gorčinu?

1470
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oprostili ste ima.

1471
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nima ni gorčine ni ništa.

1472
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nikakve.

1473
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja koga klela samo tri mjeseca.

1474
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam im govorila balije.

1475
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Posle više neću.

1476
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bože ti mene oprosti.

1477
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neću više ni to govoriti.

1478
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su za mene muslimani.

1479
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki će odgovare šta je ko radi.

1480
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaka vam časa.

1481
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to je tako.

1482
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ima ovde ovoj knjigi.

1483
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima svjetvo riječi.

1484
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:44,320
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam puno.

